<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-56-0232 </DOCNO><TEXT>Discussion is presented of the new Italian National Energy Plan, releasedin July 1988. The main objectives of the plan are to: achieve energysavings through improvements in energy efficiency in all sectors, rationaluse of energy in energy-intensive sectors, development of cogenerationand district heating systems; reduce atmospheric pollution from electricpower plants; develop domestic energy supplies, and diversify energysupplies. 2 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>